 We need to construct a map 
\begin_inset Formula $\widetilde{\psi}\colon N\to E$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\widetilde{\psi}\varphi=\psi$
\end_inset

.
 To do this, consider the pushout module
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E+_{M}N=(E\times N)\slash\{(\psi(u),-\varphi(u))\mid u\in M\}
\]

\end_inset

together its natural maps 
\begin_inset Formula $\iota_{1}\colon E\to E+_{M}N$
\end_inset

