\end{align*}

\end_inset

implies 
\begin_inset Formula $u-\widetilde{\pi}\pi(u)\in\ker\pi=E$
\end_inset

.
 This implies 
\begin_inset Formula $M=E+\widetilde{\pi}(M\slash E)$
\end_inset

